In 2012 Lucas Oil Stadium In Indianapolis, I was a guest of Icon International, Playboy and Maxim. I spent a week in Indiana of pure bliss full of Pre- Super Bowl activities and private parties with a crew of Icon guest, a great crew of cool peeps. Hey Y'All - I see you in Scottsdale this year-miss you. 

Lastly, Eli Manning won two Super Bowl championships (2008 and 2012) both years I was there. OMG. Thanks #elimanning for this amazing gift of a signed football from you. I still treasure it today.

In memory and honor of 
LANCE REDDICK 1962-2023

Lance was known for his work in HBO's 'The Wire' and the 'John Wick' movie franchise. This morning he tragically left this earth way too soon, they are saying he died of natural causes at the young age of 60. 

Life is truly about those defining moments and memories we make along the way. This was a special memory- Here we are at my home back in 2015 filming a movie with Lance playing the lead character. We had a blast during those few days together. Lance was kind, funny and a down to earth gentleman. 

Prayers and condolences going out to his family, friends and colleagues as this is shocking news for all of us. RIP.
